response.overview: Stowing away after a failed con, a pair of swindlers end up on El Dorado, the fabled "city of gold", where they quickly get in over their heads when they are mistaken as gods by the inhabitants.
response.tagline: They came for the gold. They stayed for the adventure.
response.title: The Road to El Dorado
